##Encontramos los subconjuntos
subset <- is.subset(rgorden, rgorden)


#Analizar Triangular 

subset[lower.tri(subset, diag = T)] <- NA

##Buscamos las redundantes

redund <- colSums(subset, na.rm = T) >= 1

which(redund)
